    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，Customer作为参与者，Trip作为系统模块。查询动作是Customer主动发起的，我理解为Customer发送suitable_trips请求给Trip，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Customer",
        "Trip",
        "suitable_trips"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，而且Customer是外部用户，建议用actor而不是普通participant来标识。Trip收到请求后要激活处理，处理完再返回结果。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Customer",
        "Trip",
        "activate",
        "deactivate"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我把Customer设为actor，Trip设为participant。先画Customer到Trip的suitable_trips调用，然后激活Trip的生命线。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Customer",
        "Trip",
        "suitable_trips",
        "activate Trip"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，返回消息需要明确一点。Trip处理完后要有一条虚线返回给Customer，表示异步回调或者响应完成。",
      "elements_involved": [
